| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-6211 — Recovery Inhibition (shinyhunters)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 78013547-b50d-52ac-bc68-e0488132a5b6"
index=* sourcetype=endpoint*
| where (CommandLine="*recoveryenabled no*" OR CommandLine="*bootstatuspolicy ignoreallfailures*") AND (process="*\bcdedit.exe")
